glosses: Oglala Lakota (member of a subtribe of the Lakota people, who belong to the Great Sioux Nation)
Ogilby's duiker, Cephalophus ogilbyi (West African species of antelope)
Ogoni (member of SE Nigerian ethnic group)
Oghuz Turk (member of an ancient Turkic nation who ruled Central Asia from about 8th to 12th century A.D.)
